<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us - MayankAI</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: #f5f5f7;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #1d1d1f;
        }

        nav {
            background: white;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e7;
            padding: 16px 0;
        }

        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .back-btn {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            color: #5856d6;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        .content-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 48px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #1d1d1f;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #6e6e73;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 32px;
        }

        .contact-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .contact-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .contact-value {
            color: #5856d6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .contact-value:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="/" class="back-btn">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
                </svg>
                Back to Home
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <div class="content-card">
            <h1>Contact Us</h1>
            <p>We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have questions, feedback, or need support, feel free to reach out to us.</p>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-label">Email</div>
                    <a href="mailto:mayankkamriya305@gmail.com" class="contact-value">mayankkamriya305@gmail.com</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-label">LinkedIn</div>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mayank-kamriya/" target="_blank" class="contact-value">Connect on LinkedIn</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-label">GitHub</div>
                    <a href="https://github.com/mayankkamriya" target="_blank" class="contact-value">View on GitHub</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
